WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:09.299
Good morning, everybody. I wanted to come on today and just tell everybody a quick testimony of what God did for us a couple of years ago now.

00:00:09.300 --> 00:00:19.475
We were cleaning the rugs at the church on Saturday, and we were driving home; we were headed home.

00:00:19.476 --> 00:00:28.811
The gas gauge on the truck that we had was completely broken, and I didn't realize how low we were on gas.

00:00:28.812 --> 00:00:36.652
We were driving down the highway when, all of a sudden, the truck just went dead and ran out of gas.

00:00:36.653 --> 00:00:41.428
It was probably about 105 degrees in July; it was really hot outside.

00:00:41.429 --> 00:00:49.384
My wife was pregnant with our daughter at the time, and my son and my other daughter were in the back seat.

00:00:49.385 --> 00:01:05.112
As I pulled over, my wife asked, "What's wrong?"and I said, "I think we just ran out of gas."We started getting really nervous because it was so hot outside.

00:01:05.113 --> 00:01:19.354
I rolled down the windows and started praying in the Holy Spirit, asking God for mercy because I didn't want to get out of the truck and walk down the highway with a pregnant wife and two kids.

00:01:19.355 --> 00:01:38.732
My son was six and my daughter was 10. So I was just praying and, all of a sudden, out of nowhere, I'm holding the steering wheel and I feel this bang on the back of our truck and it jolted us forward.

00:01:38.733 --> 00:01:56.416
I thought we were rear-ended; that's how hard it was. I looked in my rearview mirror—and I'm seeing in the spirit at this time—and I see an angel smiling at me in the spirit realm, grinning from ear to ear.

00:01:56.417 --> 00:02:00.098
He was this big, heavy-set guy, kind of like I am; he was chunky-looking.

00:02:00.099 --> 00:02:10.872
He had huge, massive wings spanned out on the back, and he had a hold of my tailgate.

00:02:10.873 --> 00:02:20.891
All of a sudden, we started moving supernaturally down the road; he started pushing us faster and faster.

00:02:20.892 --> 00:02:35.067
I was shook up at this time; I was in shock. We started moving, and as I held onto the steering wheel, I turned my blinker on to get back on the highway.

00:02:35.068 --> 00:02:40.378
My wife's like, "My God, what's going on?"We were all just freaking out.

00:02:40.379 --> 00:02:46.328
We were going faster and faster, and I'm in the left-hand lane.

00:02:46.329 --> 00:02:54.018
We were gathering so much speed that we started passing people in the right-hand lane all the way down.

00:02:54.019 --> 00:03:03.169
That angel pushes us three miles to the next gas station. We exit the highway.

00:03:03.170 --> 00:03:13.859
We stop at the stoplight. He pushes us through the stoplight down the street another block or so.

00:03:13.860 --> 00:03:24.890
We turn right and then we go right into the gas station, and he yanks the tailgate of that truck, and we stop in front of the pump.

00:03:24.891 --> 00:03:30.460
When he did, we all just started screaming and praising God at the pump.

00:03:30.461 --> 00:03:41.775
People at the other pumps were looking at us like, "What is wrong with them?"you know, but we were just so excited that we just had an angelic visitation.

00:03:41.776 --> 00:03:51.281
My kids didn't see it, nor did my wife, but we all felt the truck moving. We were going so fast down the highway; everybody knew it.

00:03:51.282 --> 00:03:56.252
When we got to the pump at the gas station, we all just started worshiping.

00:03:56.253 --> 00:04:06.121
It was just a really cool moment. Everybody was just like, "Wow,"and we all just started laughing. We just got so full of joy at what God just did.

00:04:06.122 --> 00:04:17.757
So I just wanted to come on and tell everybody this testimony about what happened for my children and me, that the Lord took care of us.

00:04:17.758 --> 00:04:24.183
We didn't have to have my wife go through it by herself in the middle of the heat and do all that.

00:04:24.184 --> 00:04:33.246
It was a dangerous situation and he came through for us. So I just wanted to tell everybody about the goodness of God and what He does.

00:04:33.247 --> 00:04:42.660
If you believe, all things are possible to him that believes. And nothing's too big for God.

00:04:42.661 --> 00:04:46.685
I have testimony after testimony that I'm going to document.

00:04:46.686 --> 00:04:52.806
I'm going to put them on here so people can hear about the goodness of God and what He's still doing today.

00:04:52.807 --> 00:05:05.034
Jesus Christ is the same yesterday, today, and forever. And the miracles that He did two thousand years ago, He will still do today if you believe Him for them.

00:05:05.035 --> 00:05:13.446
I believe with all my heart. I've seen it time and time again, and I'm going to tell you about each one of them. Stay tuned.

00:05:13.447 --> 00:05:26.518
Thank you for watching, and if you could give us a thumbs up, a like, or a share, it really helps us with the algorithms on YouTube.

00:05:26.519 --> 00:05:31.638
They try to suppress some of my videos and I'm trying to get them out there for the people.

00:05:31.639 --> 00:05:37.875
I really believe God put me on this platform to help folks in these last days.

00:05:37.876 --> 00:05:43.042
There's a lot that I have inside of me to help people, and I want to get it out there.

00:05:43.043 --> 00:05:53.320
So if you could help us if you want to. All right, thank you so much for watching. Have a blessed day. Bye.

